Package: RegCompassR
Title: Multiome-Supported Reaction Capacity and Constrained Flux Potential Analysis
Version: 1.0.0
Authors@R: c(person(given = "RegCompass", family = "Developers", role = c("aut", "cre"), email = "dev@example.com"))
Description: Provides a Layer 1 workflow for annotated Seurat v4 RNA+ATAC multiome objects, including raw RNA count extraction, sample-aware cell-type micropooling, pool-summed logCPM normalization, robust GPR-aware reaction capacity potential, cell-type Q95 calibration, reaction confidence, and diagnostics. Version 1.0 documents a Layer 2 design that uses Layer 1 capacity as priors, bound modifiers, penalties, and reaction-selection evidence for selected stoichiometrically constrained and balance-penalized flux-potential optimization without claiming measured flux.
